'''Killik silk''' was a lustrous and durable [[Silk/Legends|fabric]] that was woven by the secretions of specific [[Killik/Legends|Killik]] [[Species/Legends|species]] within [[The Colony]].

In [[36 ABY]], [[Alema Rar]], a [[Dark Jedi/Legends|Dark Jedi]] and a [[Joiner]], wearing a midnight blue, skin tight-fitting bodysuit made of fabric when she confronted [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] on [[Woteba]].<ref name="Unseen Queen">''[[Dark Nest II: The Unseen Queen]]''</ref>

